WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.072
Information flow is the flow of information

2
00:00:03.072 --> 00:00:06.040
both ways between the vendor and the customer,

3
00:00:06.040 --> 00:00:08.249
such as the logistics staff.

4
00:00:08.249 --> 00:00:10.758
The type of information that flows between customers

5
00:00:10.758 --> 00:00:13.752
and suppliers include: quotes for supplies,

6
00:00:13.752 --> 00:00:17.341
purchase order information, delivery information

7
00:00:17.341 --> 00:00:20.883
and status of supplies, invoices on sale of supplies,

8
00:00:20.883 --> 00:00:25.541
pricing information, and customer feedback with process.

9
00:00:25.541 --> 00:00:27.981
For the supply chain to operate effectively,

10
00:00:27.981 --> 00:00:30.089
there has to be constant communication

11
00:00:30.089 --> 00:00:32.099
between supplier and customer.

